<figureCitation box="[596,692,358,382]" captionStart="Figure 1" captionStartId="5.[144,211,630,652]" captionTargetBox="[144,1102,160,597]" captionTargetId="figure-6@5.[144,1102,160,597]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Figure 1. Distributional records of terrestrial planarians from the Iberian Peninsula used for this study. Filled circles: localities with previously known species. Stars: localities with new species." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5203498" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5203498/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="887">Figure 1</figureCitation>
