<paragraph blockId="20.[213,330,420,443]" box="[213,330,420,443]" pageId="20" pageNumber="887">
<emphasis box="[213,330,420,443]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="887">Discussion</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="20.[213,1170,459,611]" pageId="20" pageNumber="887">
As was predicted in a previous paper (
<bibRefCitation author="Vila-Farre M &amp; Mateos E &amp; Sluys R &amp; Romero R" box="[635,873,459,483]" pageId="20" pageNumber="887" pagination="1 - 20" refId="ref11693" refString="Vila-Farre M, Mateos E, Sluys R, Romero R. 2008. Terrestrial planarians (Platyhelminthes, Tricladida, Terricola) from the Iberian Peninsula: new records and description of three new species. Zootaxa. 1739: 1 - 20." type="journal article" year="2008">Vila-Farré et al. 2008</bibRefCitation>
) new sampling has yielded one new locality in southern 
<collectingCountry box="[536,603,491,515]" name="Spain" pageId="20" pageNumber="887">Spain</collectingCountry>
, la Axarquía (
<tableCitation box="[761,844,491,515]" captionStart="Table 1" captionStartId="3.[144,199,1199,1221]" captionText="Table 1. List of localities with new records of terrestrial planarians in the Iberian Peninsula." pageId="20" pageNumber="887">Table 1</tableCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[856,949,491,515]" captionStart="Figure 1" captionStartId="5.[144,211,630,652]" captionTargetBox="[144,1102,160,597]" captionTargetId="figure-6@5.[144,1102,160,597]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Figure 1. Distributional records of terrestrial planarians from the Iberian Peninsula used for this study. Filled circles: localities with previously known species. Stars: localities with new species." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5203498" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5203498/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="887">Figure 1</figureCitation>
), where this species has been found under a flowerpot in a mango plantation. The origin of this population, native or introduced, is uncertain because of the anthropogenic character of the habitat.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="20.[213,368,680,704]" box="[213,368,680,704]" pageId="20" pageNumber="887">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[213,368,680,704]" pageId="20" pageNumber="887">Exotic species</emphasis>
</paragraph>
